[SPEAKER_04]: Scotland already produces 75% of its electricity from renewable sources.

408
00:31:56,759 --> 00:32:01,389
[SPEAKER_04]: We absolutely now must prioritise transport, which we have spoken about, and heat.

409
00:32:01,409 --> 00:32:04,595
